Summary: It appears to have the shape of a blimp.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Wapiti
This sighting has never been favorited.
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile driving in our rental car back to our hotel from a trip to Yellowstone Park, I took pictures while driving or we stopped to take pictures. I did not notice any object when I took the picture. But when I came home and downloaded the picture on my computer I was surprised to see this object. I would like to know what it could be.
